{"tid":1333573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[伸手黨]尖沙咀連儂牆好需要文宣組嘅協助","createTime":"2019-07-19T18:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T08:24:03.000Z","uid":228378,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"756e9cf3c8a62cd7818489ab18b55e6f528d180d","tid":1333573,"uid":228378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:15:36.000Z","msg":"同其他社區一樣<br />\n連儂牆除咗可以俾香港人互相打氣之外<br />\n仲可以增加淺藍嘅關注度 嘗試由藍轉黃<br />\n但因為地區嘅問題<br />\n再加上連儂牆位於尖東站L5出口<br />\n極近海港城/apple shop/碼頭 呢啲旅客熱點!!<br />\n所以我覺得尖沙咀嘅target<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對</span></strong></span>要包括埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">祖國嘅同胞</span></strong></span>!!<br />\n奈何簡體字嘅文宣真係少之有少啊<br />\n<br />\n有無文宣組嘅兄弟可以幫幫手啊?<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3adebdce29b6ec7c1ebed6783330f28979f4db","tid":1333573,"uid":228378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:21:30.000Z","msg":"有無人幫下手?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8010d00d16a82bb810b723a01618056eeccacfff","tid":1333573,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:23:18.000Z","msg":"太夜<br />\n聽日再講"},{"pid":"3718fc03cbaec4c11bcc48e789cdd6daae77bffd","tid":1333573,"uid":158090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:30:29.000Z","msg":"要圖?"},{"pid":"a20787097e3b3948116b61d34e12f462435f0ca6","tid":1333573,"uid":228378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3718fc03cbaec4c11bcc48e789cdd6daae77bffd","tid":1333573,"uid":158090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:30:29.000Z","msg":"要圖?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T02:26:26.000Z"